{"tid":2282250,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［圖表派，轉身快］s&p 世紀大喇叭","createTime":"2020-11-11T17:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T17:11:39.000Z","uid":320177,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4abab99df9e890dbbc4cbb3baeda8d101b197570","tid":2282250,"uid":320177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Hbh98y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Hbh98y.png&h=7cb610b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上次講到呢個世紀大喇叭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gM7UsVG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgM7UsVG.png&h=6da40b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開大日線圖睇，家下已經有半枝燭突破<br />\n但一條講緊行左幾年既阻力線，梗會有誤差<br />\n<br />\n所以我會穿3590 2天或以上先算真突破<br />\n<br />\n偷步黎講今日可以試小小。<br />\n<br />\n接下落嚟講小小利好因素<br />\n<br />\n第一係vix，升市vix跌<br />\n第二係債息率，債息升<br />\n<br />\n但都有隱憂<br />\n唔見有人大量槓桿入市<br />\n滙市好似唔多同意個股市升<br />\n<br />\n今日只係<br />\n偷步<br />\n偷步<br />\n偷步<br />\n<br />\n而且收市收唔番係3570上面，上面既野可以當冇睇過。"}]}